                    <li><strong>Provides a clear tracking of borrowed items</strong> - allows tracking of borrowed items, including who borrowed and what was borrowed.</li>
                    <li><strong>Provides proper record keeping</strong> - records all borrowed items and other details in the database so nothing gets lost or forgotten.</li>
